			<outline text="Received the new Pixel Watch and started wearing it today. Now I am re-learning the Fitbit app. I've added an entry to the Every Day Tech section of &lt;a href=&quot;http://tech.frankm.info&quot;&gt;my personal technology outline&lt;/a&gt; for the Pixel Watch." created="Fri, 14 Oct 2022 14:00:38 GMT"/>
