				<outline text="I installed &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.home-assistant.io/getting-started/&quot;&gt;Home Assistant&lt;/a&gt; on a Raspberry Pi to learn more about smart home automation and too gain more control over my smart things. Is it possible to control Samsung SmartThings items?" created="Fri, 13 Aug 2021 17:50:27 GMT"/>
				<outline text="I've been wanting to build a cluster of Raspberry Pis for some time so that I can tinker with and learn kubernetes and vmWare. &lt;a href=&quot;http://my.this.how/frankm/myTechProjects.opml#1627586396000&quot;&gt;Cluster assembly&lt;/a&gt; is complete and now I am tinkering with kubernetes. Next is to learn how persistent storage is handled." created="Fri, 06 Aug 2021 12:11:39 GMT"/>
